OL,4,BVAR controversy: Premier League
OL,5,Bexecutive says law change may be needed
OL,6, Football laws may need changing to help
OL,7, reduce VAR controversy, a Premier
OL,8, League club executive has told the BBC.
OL,10,FThe league introduced VAR this season
OL,11,Fbut a number of high-profile decisions
OL,12,Fhave been criticised over
OL,13,Finconsistencies and the time it takes.
OL,15,FHowever, on Thursday, top-flight clubs
OL,16,Fwere told that there would be no
OL,17,Fsubstantive changes this season.
OL,19,F"Issues may only be fully resolved by
OL,20,Fgreater clarity within the laws
OL,21,Fthemselves," the club executive said.
